{"type":"message","id":"a900bafe","parentId":"3ee51d17","timestamp":"2026-03-12T12:07:03.881Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"技能已经成功安装到指定目录了。","thinkingSignature":"80bdd12d39b0c3bbb80e0355a55f59298350ed7cb6069f7d8779e076c09170dd"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **技能安装完成！**\n\n已安装 `feishu-calendar-operations` 技能到：\n```\nC:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\pv-engineer\\skills\\feishu-calendar-operations\\SKILL.md\n```\n\n这个技能主要提供：\n- 日历事件完整操作（创建/修改/删除/查询）\n- 参会人管理（邀请/移除/重新邀请）\n- 权限问题排查与解决\n- 批量授权流程\n\n和你现有的 `feishu-calendar` 技能相比，这个更侧重于**事件操作流程**和**故障排查**，而原来的更侧重于**日历工具集**。可以根据需要交替使用～ ☀️"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":14180,"output":160,"cacheRead":16624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30964,"cost":{"input":0.004254,"output":0.000192,"cacheRead":0.0004987199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0049447200000000005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773317211058}}
