{"type":"message","id":"98247afc","parentId":"bad71a9d","timestamp":"2026-03-12T12:10:34.028Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger wants to create a public shared folder for skills that all agents can use. I need to find where the global skills are stored in OpenClaw and create a shared skills folder there.\n\nLet me check the OpenClaw skills directory structure.","thinkingSignature":"82fd3de4210d580c2b998a870e50397c2a17dbf9a035a6d8ae14bc438ad4a38a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pu491zvz8gog_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"Get-ChildItem -Path 'C:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\skills' -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Name\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":116,"cacheRead":23684,"cacheWrite":7223,"totalTokens":31059,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.0001392,"cacheRead":0.00071052,"cacheWrite":0.00086676,"total":0.0017272799999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773317428639}}
{"type":"message","id":"553a2ea5","parentId":"98247afc","timestamp":"2026-03-12T12:10:34.365Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pu491zvz8gog_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Name              \r\n----              \r\n1password         \r\napple-notes       \r\napple-reminders   \r\nbear-notes        \r\nblogwatcher       \r\nblucli            \r\nbluebubbles       \r\ncamsnap           \r\ncanvas            \r\nclawhub           \r\ncoding-agent      \r\ndiscord           \r\neightctl          \r\ngemini            \r\ngh-issues         \r\ngifgrep           \r\ngithub            \r\ngog               \r\ngoplaces          \r\nhealthcheck       \r\nhimalaya          \r\nimsg              \r\nmcporter          \r\nmodel-usage       \r\nnano-banana-pro   \r\nnano-pdf          \r\nnotion            \r\nobsidian          \r\nopenai-image-gen  \r\nopenai-whisper    \r\nopenai-whisper-api\r\nopenhue           \r\noracle            \r\nordercli          \r\npeekaboo          \r\nsag               \r\nsession-logs      \r\nsherpa-onnx-tts   \r\nskill-creator     \r\nslack             \r\nsongsee           \r\nsonoscli          \r\nspotify-player    \r\nsummarize         \r\nthings-mac        \r\ntmux              \r\ntrello            \r\nvideo-frames      \r\nvoice-call        \r\nwacli             \r\nweather           \r\nxurl"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":330,"aggregated":"Name              \r\n----              \r\n1password         \r\napple-notes       \r\napple-reminders   \r\nbear-notes        \r\nblogwatcher       \r\nblucli            \r\nbluebubbles       \r\ncamsnap           \r\ncanvas            \r\nclawhub           \r\ncoding-agent      \r\ndiscord           \r\neightctl          \r\ngemini            \r\ngh-issues         \r\ngifgrep           \r\ngithub            \r\ngog               \r\ngoplaces          \r\nhealthcheck       \r\nhimalaya          \r\nimsg              \r\nmcporter          \r\nmodel-usage       \r\nnano-banana-pro   \r\nnano-pdf          \r\nnotion            \r\nobsidian          \r\nopenai-image-gen  \r\nopenai-whisper    \r\nopenai-whisper-api\r\nopenhue           \r\noracle            \r\nordercli          \r\npeekaboo          \r\nsag               \r\nsession-logs      \r\nsherpa-onnx-tts   \r\nskill-creator     \r\nslack             \r\nsongsee           \r\nsonoscli          \r\nspotify-player    \r\nsummarize         \r\nthings-mac        \r\ntmux              \r\ntrello            \r\nvideo-frames      \r\nvoice-call        \r\nwacli             \r\nweather           \r\nxurl","cwd":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\pv-engineer"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773317434360}}
{"type":"message","id":"152b056d","parentId":"553a2ea5","timestamp":"2026-03-12T12:10:38.268Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"These are the built-in skills in OpenClaw. I should create a shared skills folder in a location that's accessible to all agents. The best place would be in the .openclaw workspace or a dedicated shared folder.\n\nLet me create a shared skills folder at:\n`C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\shared`\n\nThis way, all agents can access it. Let me also check if there's an existing structure I should follow.","thinkingSignature":"b532bbf6cd41d51f8e5e7a22b0631396118076f82d0cdb054f7e8c9915286f0f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n7brhtlgi3x6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p \"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\shared\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":14691,"output":134,"cacheRead":16624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31449,"cost":{"input":0.004407299999999999,"output":0.0001608,"cacheRead":0.0004987199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00506682}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773317434364}}
