{"type":"message","id":"cca97c37","parentId":"e90c9cb6","timestamp":"2026-03-12T12:10:43.249Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I created the shared folder. Now let me add a README to explain how to use it.","thinkingSignature":"3f1e09c7a1b93a8a67a362c3ae4c25aac8efe803480d1995ea1960ce52568a3d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yourbkp8w3tc_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 公共技能共享文件夹\n\n此文件夹中的技能可供所有 Agent 使用。\n\n## 添加新技能\n\n将技能的 `SKILL.md` 文件放入此文件夹，格式：\n\n```\nshared/\n├── SKILL.md          # 技能文件\n└── (其他资源文件)     # 可选\n```\n\n## 技能格式\n\nSKILL.md 需要包含 YAML frontmatter：\n\n```yaml\n---\nname: skill-name\ndescription: 技能描述（触发条件）\n---\n```\n\n## 示例\n\n参考现有技能：\n- `C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\pv-engineer\\skills\\feishu-calendar-operations\\SKILL.md`\n```\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\shared\\README.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":14892,"output":210,"cacheRead":16624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31726,"cost":{"input":0.0044675999999999995,"output":0.000252,"cacheRead":0.0004987199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005218319999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773317438547}}
